structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 9. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 3351a-19.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: City attorney in cities of the third class to represent trustees of police and firemen's pension fund.
